org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.impl

Class OpenPackageServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dataconservancy.packaging.tool.impl.OpenPackageServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OpenPackageService

    public class OpenPackageServiceImpl
extends Object
implements OpenPackageService
    Service for opening a package. A package is assumed to be a possibly compressed archive that contains a set of files all under a base directory and that set of files includes a serialized package state at a particular location.
